    "First 30 probes carry over verbatim from chainlink #140 Sub B",
    "(state/spec/chainlink-138-sub-b-recon.md + the probes.yaml that",
    "shipped with PR #167). Categorized as 'path-citation' since the",
    "scoring metric here is 'is the expected_path a substring of any",
    "returned path in the top-10'.",
    "",
    "Probes 31-49 are new additions targeting ColBERT's predicted",
    "advantage on rare-token / fingerprint / symbol-reference",
    "queries. 'colbert-favorable' = error fingerprints + function",
    "symbol refs; 'rare-token' = exact path / PR / chainlink-ID refs.",
    "",
    "Each probe scores 1/0 based on whether ANY of its expected_paths",
    "is a substring of ANY top-10 returned path. Hit-rate@10 is the",
    "primary metric; MRR@10 is computed against the FIRST matching",
    "expected_path's rank."
